snippet.title: The REAL Reason Behind Johnny Depp and Amber Heard divorce
snippet.description:
In this video we are going to discuss the real reason behind johnny depp and amber heard divorce. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
__________________________________________

On May 23, 2016 Amber Heard filed for divorce, just 15 months after her marriage with Johnny Depp in the Bahamas. Although the couple had seemed happy and the news came out of left field, Heard also filed a restraining order against the 53-year-old actor, which included allegations of domestic abuse. After much back-and-forth, they finally finalized their divorce in Jan. 2017.

What was the real reason behind their divorce? Let’s find out.
